trans-unit.source: Contains values used as identifiers by <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Provider.ITableItemProvider"></xref>.
These identifiers are used by UI Automation providers.
trans-unit.target: UI 自动化提供程序使用这些标识符。

trans-unit.source: UI Automation client applications should use the equivalent fields in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern>.
trans-unit.target: UI 自动化客户端应用程序应使用<xref:System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.TableItemPattern>中的等效字段

trans-unit.source: Identifies the property that retrieves all the column headers associated with a table item or cell.
trans-unit.target: 标识用于检索与表项或单元格关联的所有列标题的属性。
